# shfmt configuration for Susa CLI project
# Documentation: https://github.com/mvdan/sh

# NOTE: This project uses zsh (#!/usr/bin/env zsh)
# shfmt is configured for POSIX-compatible formatting

# Indent: 4 spaces (aligns with project style)
# -i 4

# Case indent: indent case statements
# -ci

# Binary next line: binary operators at start of line
# -bn

# Simplify code
# -s
